sec1.fu_memory: 0 - None No memory loss, or slight inconsistent forgetfulness.
sec1.fu_orient: 0.5 - Questionable Fully oriented except for slight difficulty with time relationships.
sec1.fu_judgment: 1 - Mild Moderate difficulty in handling problems, similarities, and differences; social judgment usually maintained.
sec1.fu_commun: 0 - None Independent function at usual level in job, shopping, volunteer and social groups.
sec1.fu_homehobb: 0 - None Life at home, hobbies, and intellectual interests well maintained.

sec2.fu_comport: 0.5 - Questionable Questionable changes in comportment, empathy, appropriateness of actions.
sec2.fu_cdrlang: 1 - Mild Moderate word finding difficulty in speech; cannot name objects in environment; reduced phrase length and/or agrammatical speech; and/or reduced comprehension in conversation and reading.
